<li id="cite_note-Heap_1988-8"><b><a href="#cite_ref-Heap_1988_8-0" title="">^</a></b> <cite style="font-style:normal" class="book" id="CITEREFHeap.2C_M.1988">Heap, M. (1988). <i><a href="http://www.mheap.com/nlp1.pdf" class="external text" title="http://www.mheap.com/nlp1.pdf" rel="nofollow">Neuro-linguistic programming, In M. Heap (Ed.) Hypnosis: Current Clinical, Experimental and Forensic Practices</a></i>. London: Croom Helm<span class="printonly">. <a href="http://www.mheap.com/nlp1.pdf" class="external free" title="http://www.mheap.com/nlp1.pdf" rel="nofollow">http://www.mheap.com/nlp1.pdf</a></span>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=Neuro-linguistic+programming%2C+In+M.+Heap+%28Ed.%29+Hypnosis%3A+Current+Clinical%2C+Experimental+and+Forensic+Practices&amp;rft.aulast=Heap%2C+M.&amp;rft.au=Heap%2C+M.&amp;rft.date=1988&amp;rft.place=London&amp;rft.pub=Croom+Helm&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.mheap.com%2Fnlp1.pdf&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Representational_systems_(NLP)"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
